{OPENAGHMATHJAX()}u{OPENAGHMATHJAX}{OPENAGHMATHJAX()}_{1}{OPENAGHMATHJAX} i
{OPENAGHMATHJAX()}u{OPENAGHMATHJAX}{OPENAGHMATHJAX()}_{2}{OPENAGHMATHJAX} tworzą boki trójkąta prostokątnego
